// Vitest Snapshot v1, https://vitest.dev/guide/snapshot.html

exports[`TermsOfServiceComponent Test > should match snapshot 1`] = `"<section class="py-16 px-4"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-8 space-y-12"><header class="flex flex-col gap-2"><p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary"> Stonemark Legal </p><h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-text leading-tight"> Terms of Service </h1><p class="text-base text-text-muted"> Last updated: November 17, 2025 </p></header><article aria-label="Terms of Service sections" class="flex flex-col gap-6"><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> Platform Objective </h2></div><p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed"> Stonemark is a platform designed to help users discover, document and share information about historical and cultural landmarks. Our goal is to make heritage data more accessible, encourage responsible exploration, and support community contributions that enrich public knowledge. </p></section><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> Rules of Use </h2></div><ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-text-muted leading-relaxed pl-5 list-disc marker:text-primary"><li>Use the platform lawfully and respectfully toward other users and local communities.</li><li>Do not upload or share content that is illegal, defamatory, obscene, or infringes third-party rights.</li><li>Provide accurate, honest information when submitting records, and clearly mark opinions or uncertain details.</li><li>Do not attempt to harm, scrape, or otherwise interfere with the platform's operation or security.</li><li>Follow any site-specific instructions for contributing photographs, location data, or metadata.</li></ul></section><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> User Responsibilities </h2></div><p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4"> Users are responsible for their own actions and the content they submit. This includes: </p><ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-text-muted leading-relaxed pl-5 list-disc marker:text-primary"><li>Ensuring any content you contribute is accurate, lawful and does not violate privacy or intellectual property rights.</li><li>Keeping your account credentials secure and notifying us promptly of any unauthorized access.</li><li>Respecting site guidance about sensitive locations, private property, or restricted areas.</li></ul></section><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> Platform Responsibilities </h2></div><p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4"> Stonemark strives to maintain a reliable and useful service. Our responsibilities include: </p><ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-text-muted leading-relaxed pl-5 list-disc marker:text-primary"><li>Maintaining the availability and security of the platform within reasonable operational limits.</li><li>Reviewing and acting on reports of unlawful or policy-violating content, including removal when necessary.</li><li>Protecting user privacy in accordance with our Privacy Policy.</li></ul></section><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> Reporting and Enforcement </h2></div><p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed"> If you see content that violates rules or is otherwise concerning, please report it using the platform's reporting tools or contact support. We may remove or restrict content and suspend accounts that breach these Terms. </p></section><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> Limitations and Disclaimers </h2></div><p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed"> The platform provides user-contributed information which may be incomplete or inaccurate. Stonemark does not guarantee the completeness or accuracy of contributed data and is not responsible for decisions you make based on it. Use your judgment and verify important details independently. </p></section><section class="bg-surface-alt border border-border rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><h2 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-text"> Contact </h2></div><p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed"> For questions about these Terms, reports or appeals, please visit <a href="/contact" class="text-info font-semibold underline decoration-2 decoration-info/60 hover:text-primary hover:decoration-primary/60 transition-colors">our contact page</a> or consult the Privacy Policy for data-related concerns. </p></section></article></div></section>"`;
